<br>
You tell n00b_beggar_01 &quot;I could use some spiderling silks.  If you get me a stack, I will give you a decent weapon.&quot;<br>
n00b_beggar_01 tells you &quot;ok where u get silks&quot;<br>
You tell n00b_beggar_01 &quot;Try the spiderlings, over by FP zone&quot;<br>
n00b_beggar_01 tells you &quot;ok i'm near at zone&quot;<br>
You tell n00b_beggar_01 &quot;Good.  Now look for a spiderling.&quot;<br>
n00b_beggar_01 tells you &quot;it didn't have ne silk.&quot;<br>
You tell n00b_beggar_01b &quot;Sometimes they don't drop silks.  Keep trying, you'll get some.&quot;<br>
n00b_beggar_01 tells you &quot;i got 3 silk dont c ne more spiders&quot;<br>
You tell n00b_beggar_01 &quot;They'll spawn, don't worry.  Don't forget to keep the other stuff that drops and sell it to the merchants at the Inn.  The money will all add up.&quot;<br>
n00b_beggar_01 tells you &quot;o ok&quot;<br>
n00b_beggar_01 tells you &quot;ok i have 7 silks is tat enuf&quot; <br>
You tell n00b_beggar_01 &quot;Sorry, I really need a whole stack.&quot;<br>
n00b_beggar_01 tells you &quot;i have 11.2 silks is that enuf&quot; <br>
n00b_beggar_01 tells you &quot;i hav 12.1327 silks is tat enuf&quot;<br>
<br>
I have ignore reserved for those with malicious intent, and I have been fortunate to have not met anyone of that sort.  Deep down I'm a sucker, and don't have the heart to put someone on ignore for just being a nitwit.  So it's around this point where I break down and have the n00b give me whatever silks they got in exchange for some half-decent weapon...<br>
